docs {
  # Virtual Dollar Cards

  These endpoints require email verification and BillXpress `tier_3`.

  Amount rules:

  - Creation and funding quotes accept `amountNgn`.
  - Withdrawal quotes accept `amountUsd`.
  - Always display the returned quote totals.
  - Never calculate exchange rates or fees on the frontend.
}

vars {
  cardId: paste-card-id-here
}
